  <h1>CSS Typography Example</h1>

  <p>Typography plays a key role in web design. You can <mark>highlight important text</mark> using the <code>&lt;mark&gt;</code> tag for emphasis and accessibility.</p>

  <p>Modern web design often includes custom fonts and <mark>clean spacing</mark> to improve readability.</p>

  <div class="highlight-section">
    <p>Did you know? The <mark>mark</mark> tag is especially useful for highlighting search terms in a document!</p>
